# NorDug Presentation - Design System

## Colors (CSS Variables)

| Variable | Value | Use |
|----------|-------|-----|
| `--accent` | #FF6B35 | Headings, highlights, borders |
| `--accent-bg` | rgba(255,107,53,0.15) | Stat boxes, accent cards |
| `--text-white` | #ffffff | Body text |
| `--text-gray` | #cccccc | Secondary text |
| `--text-dim` | #888888 | Dim text (dates, footers) |
| `--card-bg` | rgba(40,40,40,0.9) | Card background |
| `--card-border` | rgba(255,107,53,0.3) | Card borders |

## Semantic Colors

- `.accent` – orange emphasis
- `.red` – #ff6666 (warnings, crisis slides)
- `.green` – #44cc44 (success, positive)
- `.card.orange` – accent left border
- `.card.red` – red left border
- `.card.green` – green left border

## Typography

- **Font:** Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Base size:** 22px (Reveal.js)
- **h1:** 2em, 900 weight
- **h2:** 1.5em, 700 weight
- **h3/h4:** 1.2em / 1em, 600 weight

## Images

- **Logo:** `images/dEdge.png` – top-right on content slides
- **Diagrams:** `diagrams/*.svg` – max-height 350px in `.diagram` container
